# Operational Project — AI Agent Roles

This Django 6.0 project uses multi-tenancy (django-tenants), HTMX, and Unfold admin. Agents apply by task and file context.

## Agent Roles

| Role | When It Applies | Skill |
|------|-----------------|-------|
| **Software Analyst** | Analysis, requirements, scope, edge cases | `software-analyst` |
| **Planner** | Breaking work into execution plans | `planner` |
| **Django Developer** | Python, models, views, URLs, migrations | `django-developer` |
| **Frontend Developer** | HTML, HTMX, CSS, JavaScript | `frontend-developer` |

## Project Stack

- **Backend**: Django 6.0, django-tenants, django-unfold, PostgreSQL
- **Frontend**: HTML, HTMX (hypermedia), vanilla JS, CSS
- **Templates**: `templates/` (base), `apps/*/templates/` (per-app)

